{"tid":2411980,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"港男港女對待動物嘅分別","createTime":"2021-02-17T17:33:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T04:10:23.000Z","uid":324681,"like":4,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ae8d3a8414d42de9eeb53741c1e4bd5756d87295","tid":2411980,"uid":324681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T17:33:06.000Z","msg":"港男普遍對動物唔會有憐憫之心，死由得佢死，病由得佢病，有D會虐待動物嚟娛樂。<br />\n部份會欺凌動物港男都係欺善怕惡。<br />\n<br />\n港女普遍對動物存有偏私之心，口說大愛，但寵物必須純種，拒絕混種，愛，只愛貓狗，其他動物就係食物。<br />\n大部份港女養狗都養埋晒哥基柴犬茶杯貴婦比熊。。。。對唐狗就望都唔望一眼。"},{"pid":"96a4e4fb3daec8356c6c48ab155190cbf9984aeb","tid":2411980,"uid":48080,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T17:34:23.000Z","msg":"想問下樓主統計咗幾多人先得出呢個結論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"affe317e223ac31a184e3d92fa8030c3e040e93b","tid":2411980,"uid":57255,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T17:36:43.000Z","msg":"on9你話係就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"2d6a3902709000b9370ea0dc1fe30193fda4a7d4","tid":2411980,"uid":52539,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T17:40:52.000Z","msg":"樓主識d人全部都係咁上下 好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全部都npc黎"},{"pid":"666674b21ca1a846e93b516cf1c1cafe9ef8af76","tid":2411980,"uid":203198,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T17:41:05.000Z","msg":"睇第一句就知樓主弱智 此po已完"},{"pid":"a3f6ad3c384c0c677106fdbcf6dee8ca17acf7e0","tid":2411980,"uid":126648,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T17:43:50.000Z","msg":"日日都有PR批鬥港男港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78be556d09f8e2e459272775a7f5a73c3d2c29fb","tid":2411980,"uid":275114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"96a4e4fb3daec8356c6c48ab155190cbf