like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T18:54:36.000Z","msg":"我好似唔記得咗之前放貓仔落去洗衣機嗰個係男人定女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人可以話我知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想知樓主點解咁輕易得出啲咁嘅結論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867c3c317f7504b294f54d585f503b7ed1749cd3","tid":2411980,"uid":299372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T04:07:23.000Z","msg":"香港人其實好多都好錫寵物，畢竟多少受過英國文化影響<br />\n就算唔錫唔鍾意，都唔會去傷害<br />\n(當然都有棄養同虐待既死仆街，我覺得係支那種黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n講動保，不如望下支那先<br />\n連防上虐待動物法都未有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係想拎呢樣野黎分化香港人下嘛？"},{"pid":"65af98fa5508c30ce70285fa7a8beb88da99a611","tid":2411980,"uid":153144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T04:10:23.000Z","msg":"港女對動物既愛就係影相打卡"}]}